Setup Phase
- Load file
- Create new game

Play Phase
- Call
- Raise [amount]
- Fold
- Save [filename]
- Exit

Game Result Display
Would you like a new game (y/n)?

Reshuffling Phase
- Add fund [name] [amount]
- Add new player [name] [wealth]
- Remove player [name]
- Save [filename]
- Exit
- Start (new game)


Saving and Loading
- save in play phase will load into play phase
- save in reshuffling phase will load into Game Result Display and new game (y/n)